<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Custom Legal Lease Agreement</title>
  <style>
    /* PDF-Optimized Custom Legal Template */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    @page {
      size: Letter;
      margin: 1in;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Garamond', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 11.5pt;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: white;
    }

    .contract-container {
      max-width: 8.5in;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
    }

    /* Elegant Header with Border */
    .legal-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 45px;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 3px double #2c3e50;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .legal-header h1 {
      font-size: 22pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .legal-header .subtitle {
      font-size: 13pt;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #555555;
    }

    .legal-header .meta {
      font-size: 10pt;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      border-top: 1px solid #2c3e50;
    }

    .meta-item {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 20px;
    }

    /* Decorative Section Divider */
    .section-divider {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    .section-divider::before,
    .section-divider::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      width: 40%;
      height: 1px;
      background: #2c3e50;
    }

    .section-divider::before {
      left: 0;
    }

    .section-divider::after {
      right: 0;
    }

    .section-divider-text {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0 20px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555555;
    }

    /* Parties Section with Elegant Border */
    .parties-section {
      margin: 35px 0;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 2px solid #2c3e50;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
    }

    .parties-intro {
      text-align: justify;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .party-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .party-block {
      padding: 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid #2c3e50;
      background: white;
    }

    .party-heading {
      font-size: 11pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .party-details {
      padding-left: 15px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .parties-footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #cccccc;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555555;
    }

    /* Section Headers with Roman Numerals */
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 35px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2c3e50;
    }

    .section-roman {
      flex: 0 0 80px;
      font-size: 18pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .section-title {
      flex: 1;
      font-size: 14pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .subsection-header {
      font-size: 11pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 20px 0 12px 0;
      color: #333333;
    }

    /* Info Table with Elegant Styling */
    .info-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: separate;
      border-spacing: 0;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border: 1px solid #2c3e50;
    }

    .info-table tr:nth-child(odd) {
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .info-table tr:nth-child(even) {
      background: white;
    }

    .info-table td {
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
    }

    .info-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .info-table .label-cell {
      width: 35%;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 9pt;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .info-table .value-cell {
      font-size: 10.5pt;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    /* Legal Paragraphs */
    .legal-paragraph {
      text-align: justify;
      text-indent: 0.5in;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .legal-paragraph.no-indent {
      text-indent: 0;
    }

    .legal-paragraph.centered {
      text-align: center;
      text-indent: 0;
    }

    /* Numbered Lists with Enhanced Styling */
    .legal-list {
      margin: 18px 0 18px 0.75in;
      list-style-type: lower-alpha;
    }

    .legal-list.numbered {
      list-style-type: decimal;
    }

    .legal-list.roman {
      list-style-type: lower-roman;
    }

    .legal-list li {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-left: 12px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    /* Witnesseth with Ornamental Style */
    .witnesseth {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-variant: small-caps;
      margin: 40px 0;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      position: relative;
    }

    .witnesseth::before,
    .witnesseth::after {
      content: '◆';
      margin: 0 20px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    /* Recitals with Elegant Formatting */
    .recitals {
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 25px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #2c3e50;
      border-right: 4px solid #2c3e50;
    }

    .recital {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 50px;
      text-indent: -50px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .recital strong {
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    /* Custom Legal Content Area */
    .custom-legal-content {
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 35px;
      min-height: 400px;
      background: white;
      border: 2px dashed #2c3e50;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .custom-legal-content h1,
    .custom-legal-content h2,
    .custom-legal-content h3 {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
    }

    .custom-legal-content h1 {
      font-size: 16pt;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2c3e50;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .custom-legal-content h2 {
      font-size: 14pt;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .custom-legal-content h3 {
      font-size: 12pt;
    }

    .custom-legal-content p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      text-align: justify;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    .custom-legal-content ul,
    .custom-legal-content ol {
      margin: 18px 0 18px 45px;
    }

    .custom-legal-content li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }

    /* Emphasis Styles */
    .all-caps {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .emphasis {
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Callout Box */
    .legal-callout {
      margin: 25px 0;
      padding: 20px 25px;
      background: #fff9e6;
      border: 2px solid #d4af37;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .legal-callout-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11pt;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* Signature Section */
    .signature-section {
      margin-top: 40px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .signature-intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 11pt;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-top: 2px solid #2c3e50;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2c3e50;
    }

    .signature-blocks {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .signature-block {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      padding: 25px;
      border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      background: #fafbfc;
    }

    .signature-label {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .signature-line {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2c3e50;
      width: 400px;
      height: 50px;
      margin: 20px 0 8px 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    .signature-line img {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 5px;
      left: 0;
      max-height: 40px;
    }

    .signature-name {
      font-size: 11pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .signature-title {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555555;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .signature-date-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .date-label {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .date-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #2c3e50;
      width: 220px;
      padding: 6px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Notary Section */
    .notary-section {
      margin-top: 55px;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 4px double #2c3e50;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .notary-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 13pt;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .notary-text {
      line-height: 2.2;
      margin-bottom: 35px;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
    }

    .notary-seal-area {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .notary-seal {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      border: 3px solid #2c3e50;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: white;
    }

    .notary-signature-area {
      flex: 1;
      margin-left: 30px;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .legal-footer {
      margin-top: 55px;
      padding: 25px;
      border-top: 3px double #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10pt;
      line-height: 1.9;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .legal-footer .emphasis-text {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11pt;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Print Optimizations */
    @media print {
      body {
        print-color-adjust: exact;
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      }
      .page-break {
        page-break-before: always;
      }
    }

    /* Utility Classes */
    .text-center { text-align: center; }
    .text-right { text-align: right; }
    .text-justify { text-align: justify; }
    .bold { font-weight: 700; }
    .italic { font-style: italic; }
    .underline { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="contract-container">
    <!-- ELEGANT HEADER -->
    <div class="legal-header">
      <h1>Short-Term Rental Agreement</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">Vacation Rental Contract</div>
      <div class="meta">
        <span class="meta-item"><strong>Booking No:</strong> <%= leaseNumber %></span>
        <span class="meta-item"><strong>Start:</strong> <%= startDate %></span>
        <span class="meta-item"><strong>End:</strong> <%= endDate %></span>
        <span class="meta-item"><strong>Date:</strong> <%= currentDate %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PARTIES SECTION -->
    <div class="parties-section">
      <p class="parties-intro">
        <span class="all-caps">This Lease Agreement</span> (hereinafter referred to as the "Agreement"),
        made and entered into on this <strong><%= signedDate %></strong>, is by and between the parties
        identified below:
      </p>

      <div class="party-grid">
        <div class="party-block">
          <div class="party-heading">Landlord (Property Owner)</div>
          <div class="party-details">
            <strong><%= landlordName %></strong><br>
            <%= landlordAddress %><br>
            Email: <%= landlordEmail %><br>
            Telephone: <%= landlordPhone %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="party-block">
          <div class="party-heading">Tenant (Lessee)</div>
          <div class="party-details">
            <strong><%= tenantName %></strong><br>
            Email: <%= tenantEmail %><br>
            Telephone: <%= tenantPhone %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if (isExternalOwner && managementCompanyName) { %>
      <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding: 20px; background: white; border: 2px solid #2c3e50; border-radius: 4px;">
        <div class="party-heading">Property Management Company (Authorized Agent)</div>
        <div class="party-details" style="margin-top: 12px;">
          <strong><%= managementCompanyName %></strong><br>
          <%= managementCompanyAddress %><br>
          Email: <%= managementCompanyEmail %><br>
          Telephone: <%= managementCompanyPhone %><br>
          <em style="color: #666; font-size: 9.5pt; margin-top: 8px; display: block;">Acting as Authorized Agent for Property Owner</em>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <% if (coTenants && coTenants.length > 0) { %>
      <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding: 20px; background: white; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">
        <div class="party-heading">Additional Co-Tenants</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
          <% coTenants.forEach(coTenant => { %>
          <div style="padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-left: 3px solid #2c3e50; background: #f8f9fa;">
            <strong><%= coTenant.name %></strong><br>
            <span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #555555;">
              Email: <%= coTenant.email %> | Phone: <%= coTenant.phone %>
              <% if (coTenant.occupation) { %><br>Occupation: <%= coTenant.occupation %><% } %>
            </span>
          </div>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <p class="parties-footer">
        The Landlord and Tenant are hereinafter collectively referred to as the "Parties"
        and individually as a "Party."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- WITNESSETH -->
    <div class="witnesseth">Witnesseth</div>

    <!-- RECITALS -->
    <div class="recitals">
      <div class="recital">
        <strong>WHEREAS,</strong>
        <% if (hasUnitOwner) { %>
          the Landlord is the lawful owner of <% if (unitNumber) { %>Unit <strong><%= unitNumber %></strong><% } else { %>a residential unit<% } %>
          located within <% if (propertyName) { %><strong><%= propertyName %></strong>,<% } %> a property located at <strong><%= propertyAddress %></strong>
          (hereinafter referred to as the "Property");
        <% } else if (isExternalOwner) { %>
          the Landlord, as authorized owner/manager<% if (propertyName) { %> of <strong><%= propertyName %></strong><% } %>,
          has the legal right to lease rental property located at <strong><%= propertyAddress %></strong>
          (hereinafter referred to as the "Property");
        <% } else { %>
          the Landlord is the lawful owner and possessor of rental property
          <% if (propertyName) { %><strong><%= propertyName %></strong> <% } %>located at <strong><%= propertyAddress %></strong>
          (hereinafter referred to as the "Property");
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <div class="recital">
        <strong>WHEREAS,</strong> the Tenant desires to rent
        <% if (hasUnitOwner && unitNumber) { %>
          Unit <strong><%= unitNumber %></strong> at the Property
        <% } else { %>
          the Property
        <% } %>
        from the Landlord for short-term
        purposes from <strong><%= startDate %></strong> to <strong><%= endDate %></strong>
        in accordance with the terms and conditions hereinafter set forth;
      </div>
      <div class="recital">
        <strong>WHEREAS,</strong> the Landlord is willing to lease the Premises to the Tenant upon the terms,
        covenants, and conditions contained in this Agreement;
      </div>
      <div class="recital" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
        <strong>WHEREAS,</strong> both Parties wish to set forth in writing the terms and conditions of their agreement.
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="legal-paragraph centered" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 12pt; margin: 35px 0;">
      NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants, promises, and agreements herein contained,
      and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged,
      the Parties hereto agree as follows:
    </p>

    <!-- SECTION I: BASIC INFORMATION -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-roman">I.</div>
        <div class="section-title">Fundamental Lease Information</div>
      </div>

      <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Lease Classification:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><%= leaseType %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Start Date:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><%= startDate %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">End Date:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><%= endDate %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Total Rental Amount:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><strong><%= monthlyRent %></strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Security Deposit:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><%= securityDeposit %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Rent Payment Due Date:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><%= rentDueDayOrdinal %> day of each calendar month</td>
        </tr>
        <% if (petPolicy && petPolicy.allowed) { %>
        <tr>
          <td class="label-cell">Pet Deposit:</td>
          <td class="value-cell"><%= petPolicy.deposit %></td>
        </tr>
        <% } %>
      </table>

      <% if (renewalOptions && renewalOptions.autoRenew) { %>
      <div class="legal-callout">
        <div class="legal-callout-title">⚠ Automatic Renewal Provision</div>
        <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.8;">
          This Agreement contains an automatic renewal clause. Unless either Party provides written notice
          of termination at least <strong><%= renewalOptions.noticePeriodDays %> days</strong> prior to the
          expiration date, this Agreement shall automatically renew for an additional term of
          <strong><%= renewalOptions.renewalTermMonths %> months</strong> under the same terms and conditions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <!-- SECTION II: CUSTOM LEGAL TERMS -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-roman">II.</div>
        <div class="section-title">Terms, Covenants, and Conditions</div>
      </div>

      <% if (legalTerms && legalTerms.html) { %>
      <!-- User-Provided HTML Content -->
      <div class="custom-legal-content">
        <%- legalTerms.html %>
      </div>
      <% } else if (legalTerms && legalTerms.text) { %>
      <!-- User-Provided Plain Text Content -->
      <div class="custom-legal-content">
        <p class="legal-paragraph">
          <%= legalTerms.text %>
        </p>
      </div>
      <% } else { %>
      <!-- Default Legal Terms -->
      <div class="subsection-header">2.1 Leased Premises</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The Landlord hereby agrees to lease to the Tenant, and the Tenant hereby agrees to lease from the Landlord,
        the Premises located at <strong><%= propertyAddress %></strong>, together with all rights, privileges, and
        appurtenances thereto belonging, for the term and subject to the covenants and conditions hereinafter set forth.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.2 Use and Occupancy</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The Property shall be used and occupied by the Tenant for short-term residential purposes only.
        Tenant agrees to use the Property in a responsible manner that does not disturb neighbors or damage the Property.
        Tenant shall not use or permit the use of the Property for any unlawful purpose, parties, events,
        or commercial activities without prior written consent from the Landlord.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.3 Rental Payment Obligations</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The Tenant covenants and agrees to pay to the Landlord, without demand, offset, or deduction, the sum of
        <strong><%= monthlyRent %></strong> per calendar month as rent for the Premises. Payment shall
        be made in advance on the <strong><%= rentDueDayOrdinal %></strong> day of each month during the
        term of this Agreement. All payments shall be made to the Landlord at the address specified above or at
        such other place as the Landlord may designate in writing.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.4 Security Deposit</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        Upon execution of this Agreement, the Tenant has deposited with the Landlord the sum of
        <strong><%= securityDeposit %></strong> as security for the faithful performance and observance
        by the Tenant of the terms, provisions, and conditions of this Agreement. Said deposit shall be returned
        to the Tenant, without interest, within the time period required by applicable law following termination
        of the tenancy, less any lawful deductions for damages beyond normal wear and tear, unpaid rent, or other
        charges due under this Agreement.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.5 Maintenance and Repair Obligations</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The Landlord shall maintain the structural components of the Premises in good repair and shall comply with
        all applicable building, housing, and health codes. The Tenant shall maintain the Premises in a clean and
        sanitary condition, shall dispose of all garbage and waste in a proper manner, and shall be responsible
        for any damage to the Premises caused by the Tenant's negligence or misuse.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.6 Utilities and Services</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        <% if (utilitiesIncluded) { %>
        The Landlord agrees to provide and pay for the following utilities and services: <%= utilitiesIncluded %>.
        <% } %>
        The Tenant shall be responsible for the payment of all other utilities and services furnished to the Premises
        not expressly stated herein to be the responsibility of the Landlord.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.7 Pet Provisions</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        <% if (petPolicy && petPolicy.allowed) { %>
        The Tenant is permitted to keep a maximum of <strong><%= petPolicy.maxPets %></strong> pet(s) of the following
        types: <strong><%= petPolicy.types %></strong>. The Tenant has paid a pet deposit of
        <strong><%= petPolicy.deposit %></strong> and agrees to be responsible for all damages caused by
        any pet(s). The Tenant further agrees to comply with all applicable laws and regulations regarding pet ownership.
        <% } else { %>
        No animals, birds, or pets of any kind shall be kept on or about the Premises without the prior written consent
        of the Landlord, which consent may be withheld at the Landlord's sole discretion.
        <% } %>
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.8 Assignment and Subletting Prohibition</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The Tenant shall not assign this Agreement or sublet the whole or any part of the Premises without the prior
        written consent of the Landlord. Any attempted assignment or subletting without such consent shall be void
        and shall, at the option of the Landlord, terminate this Agreement.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.9 Right of Entry</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The Landlord and Landlord's agents shall have the right to enter the Premises at all reasonable times for
        the purpose of examining or inspecting the Premises, making necessary repairs or alterations, or showing
        the Premises to prospective tenants, purchasers, or lenders. Except in cases of emergency, the Landlord
        shall provide the Tenant with reasonable advance notice of such entry.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">2.10 Termination and Surrender</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        <% if (renewalOptions && renewalOptions.noticePeriodDays) { %>
        Either Party may terminate this Agreement by providing written notice to the other Party at least
        <strong><%= renewalOptions.noticePeriodDays %> days</strong> prior to the intended termination date.
        <% } else { %>
        Either Party may terminate this Agreement by providing written notice to the other Party at least
        <strong>30 days</strong> prior to the intended termination date.
        <% } %>
        Upon termination, the Tenant shall surrender the Premises to the Landlord in the same condition as received,
        ordinary wear and tear excepted, and shall remove all personal property belonging to the Tenant.
      </p>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <!-- PAGE BREAK -->
    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <!-- SECTION III: GENERAL PROVISIONS -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-roman">III.</div>
        <div class="section-title">General Provisions</div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection-header">3.1 Entire Agreement</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        This Agreement contains the entire agreement between the Parties relating to the subject matter hereof
        and supersedes all prior agreements, negotiations, representations, or proposals, whether written or oral.
        This Agreement may not be amended or modified except by a written instrument executed by both Parties.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">3.2 Severability</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        If any provision of this Agreement shall be held to be invalid or unenforceable for any reason, the
        remaining provisions shall continue to be valid and enforceable. If a court finds that any provision
        of this Agreement is invalid or unenforceable, but that by limiting such provision it would become
        valid and enforceable, then such provision shall be deemed to be written, construed, and enforced as
        so limited.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">3.3 Waiver of Rights</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        The failure of either Party to enforce any provision of this Agreement shall not be construed as a
        waiver or limitation of that Party's right to subsequently enforce and compel strict compliance with
        every provision of this Agreement.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">3.4 Governing Law and Venue</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        This Agreement shall be governed by, construed, and enforced in accordance with the laws of the
        jurisdiction in which the Premises are located, without regard to conflicts of law principles.
        Any legal action or proceeding arising out of or relating to this Agreement shall be brought
        exclusively in the courts of competent jurisdiction in said location.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">3.5 Notices</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        All notices, requests, demands, and other communications required or permitted to be given under this
        Agreement shall be in writing and shall be deemed to have been duly given when delivered personally,
        sent by certified or registered mail (return receipt requested), or sent by a nationally recognized
        overnight courier service to the addresses set forth above or to such other address as either Party
        may designate by written notice to the other.
      </p>

      <div class="subsection-header">3.6 Binding Effect</div>
      <p class="legal-paragraph">
        This Agreement shall be binding upon and inure to the benefit of the Parties hereto and their respective
        heirs, executors, administrators, successors, and assigns, subject to the provisions herein regarding
        assignment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- SECTION DIVIDER -->
    <div class="section-divider">
      <span class="section-divider-text">Signatures Follow</span>
    </div>

    <!-- SIGNATURES -->
    <div class="signature-section">
      <div class="signature-intro">
        <strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF,</strong> the Parties have executed this Residential Lease Agreement
        as of the day and year first above written.
      </div>

      <div class="signature-blocks">
        <!-- Landlord Signature -->
        <div class="signature-block">
          <div class="signature-label">Landlord / Lessor</div>
          <div class="signature-line">
            <% if (signingMethod === 'electronic' && landlordSignatureUrl) { %>
            <img src="<%= landlordSignatureUrl %>" alt="Landlord Signature">
            <% } else if (signingMethod === 'electronic') { %>
            <span style="color: white; text-transform: none;">{{sign|1|*}}</span>
            <% } %>
          </div>
          <div class="signature-name"><strong><%= landlordName %></strong></div>
          <div class="signature-title">
            <% if (isExternalOwner) { %>
              Property Owner (or Authorized Agent)
            <% } else { %>
              Property Owner
            <% } %>
          </div>
          <div class="signature-date-row">
            <span class="date-label">Date Signed:</span>
            <div class="date-line"><% if (signingMethod === 'electronic') { %><span style="color: white; text-transform: none;">{{date|1|*}}</span><% } else { %><%= signedDate %><% } %></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tenant Signature -->
        <div class="signature-block">
          <div class="signature-label">Tenant / Lessee</div>
          <div class="signature-line">
            <% if (signingMethod === 'electronic' && tenantSignatureUrl) { %>
            <img src="<%= tenantSignatureUrl %>" alt="Tenant Signature">
            <% } else { %>
            <span style="color: white; text-transform: none;">{{sign|2|*}}</span>
            <% } %>
          </div>
          <div class="signature-name"><strong><%= tenantName %></strong></div>
          <div class="signature-title">Primary Lessee</div>
          <div class="signature-date-row">
            <span class="date-label">Date Signed:</span>
            <div class="date-line"><% if (signingMethod === 'electronic') { %><span style="color: white; text-transform: none;">{{date|2|*}}</span><% } else { %><%= signedDate %><% } %></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Co-Tenant Signatures -->
        <% if (coTenants && coTenants.length > 0) { %>
        <% coTenants.forEach((coTenant, coTenantIndex) => { %>
        <div class="signature-block">
          <div class="signature-label">Co-Tenant / Co-Lessee</div>
          <div class="signature-line">
            <span style="color: white; text-transform: none;">{{sign|<%= 3 + coTenantIndex %>|*}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="signature-name"><strong><%= coTenant.name %></strong></div>
          <div class="signature-title">Co-Lessee</div>
          <div class="signature-date-row">
            <span class="date-label">Date Signed:</span>
            <div class="date-line"><span style="color: white; text-transform: none;">{{date|<%= 3 + coTenantIndex %>|*}}</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% }); %>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- NOTARY SECTION (OPTIONAL) -->
    <% if (requiresNotarization) { %>
    <div class="notary-section">
      <div class="notary-title">Acknowledgment of Notary Public</div>

      <div class="notary-text">
        <strong>State of:</strong> _________________________________________<br>
        <strong>County of:</strong> ________________________________________<br><br>

        On this ________ day of ____________________, 20_____, before me personally appeared
        _________________________________, to me known to be the person described in and who executed
        the foregoing instrument, and acknowledged that he/she executed the same as his/her free act and deed.
      </div>

      <div class="notary-seal-area">
        <div class="notary-seal">
          (Affix Official<br>Notary Seal Here)
        </div>
        <div class="notary-signature-area">
          <div style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 700;">Signature of Notary Public:</div>
          <div style="border-bottom: 2px solid #2c3e50; width: 100%; height: 60px; margin-bottom: 10px;"></div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Print Name: _____________________________________</div>
          <div>Commission Expiration: _____________________________________</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="legal-footer">
      <div class="emphasis-text">◆ END OF LEASE AGREEMENT ◆</div>
      <p>Lease Agreement Reference Number: <strong><%= leaseNumber %></strong></p>
      <p>This instrument constitutes the entire agreement between the parties and supersedes all prior understandings.</p>
      <p style="font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px;">
        Each party acknowledges receipt of a fully executed copy of this Agreement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
